``` {.python .cell-code}
import pandas as pd
from sklearn.linear_model import LinearRegression
```
:::


::: {#479aaabb .cell execution_count=2}
``` {.python .cell-code}
df = pd.read_csv("~/Desktop/Projects/DO4DS/eda_modeling/data/penguins.csv")
```
:::


::: {#943e8c0b .cell execution_count=3}
``` {.python .cell-code}
model = LinearRegression()
x = df["bill_length_mm"]
y = df["body_mass_g"]
```
:::


::: {#02fc657c .cell execution_count=4}
``` {.python .cell-code}
model.fit(x.values.reshape(-1,1),y)
```

